tagrelator.collect.anc
Class ANCprocessor

java.lang.Object
  tagrelator.collect.anc.ANCprocessor

public class ANCprocessor
extends java.lang.Object

preprocesses the open american national corpus to an Array of ANCdocument and serializes them to files. the ANCdocument class itself contains a String Array of the words of the document in the corpus.
